Headmaster (ADMIN ROLE)
========================
Headmaster controls the entire school
Responsibilities
--------------
School profile management
Teacher hiring & mapping to subjects
Student admission & class allocation
Academic year management
Class & section creation
Subject creation
Teacher-class-subject mapping
Exam & timetable approval
Attendance & marks monitoring
Reports (pass %, attendance %, fee status)
User access control

Teacher
===================
Teacher handles academic execution
Responsibilities
--------------
View assigned classes & subjects
Mark daily attendance
Upload marks (exam-wise)
Upload assignments
View student performance
Communicate with parents

Student
============================
Student consumes academic services
Responsibilities
---------------
View personal profile
View timetable
View attendance
View marks & report card
Download assignments
Notifications